9 An Act relating to environment and natural resources;
creating the Oklahoma Biosolids Land Application
10 Research Pilot Program Act; requiring the Pilot
Program be administered by the Department of
11 Environmental Quality in cooperation with Oklahoma
State University; providing for expiration of Pilot
12 Program; listing requirements for the Pilot Program;
requiring certain annual report be submitted; listing
13 requirements for annual report; authorizing
partnerships with private landowners; limiting
14 liability; making certain exemption; requiring
certain documentation be kept; authorizing funding;
15 requiring deposit of funds in certain revolving fund;
creating the Oklahoma Biosolids Land Application
16 Research Pilot Program Act Revolving Fund; describing
fund; providing for content of fund; providing for
17 deposits and expenditures; providing for
codification; and providing an effective date.
18
